targets.rawSql:
WITH a AS (
SELECT
eventdate AS time,
decimallatitude,
decimallongitude,
geom,
COUNT(*) OVER() AS cnt
FROM explore.gbif
WHERE $__timeFilter(eventdate)
AND decimallatitude >= $minLat
AND decimallatitude <= $maxLat
AND decimallongitude >= $minLon
AND decimallongitude <= $maxLon
AND (tsv @@ websearch_to_tsquery('simple', '$search') OR NULLIF('$search', '') IS null)
), b AS (
SELECT
time,
decimallatitude,
decimallongitude,
ST_ClusterKMeans(geom, LEAST(cnt::integer, 150)) OVER() AS clusters
FROM a
)
SELECT
clusters,
COUNT(clusters) AS tooltip,
AVG(decimallatitude) AS latitude,
AVG(decimallongitude) AS longitude
FROM b
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1;

SELECT
  count(*), $__time(eventdate)
  --$__timeGroup("date",'60m')
FROM explore.gbif
WHERE $__timeFilter(eventdate)
AND decimallatitude >= $minLat
AND decimallatitude <= $maxLat
AND decimallongitude >= $minLon
AND decimallongitude <= $maxLon
AND (tsv @@ websearch_to_tsquery('simple', '$search') OR NULLIF('$search', '') IS null)
GROUP BY 2
ORDER BY 2 ASC

SELECT
  count(*), recordedby
FROM
  explore.gbif
WHERE $__timeFilter(eventdate)
AND (tsv @@ websearch_to_tsquery('simple', '$search') OR NULLIF('$search', '') IS null)
AND (recordedby IN ($recordedby) OR NULLIF(TRIM(CONCAT($recordedby)), '') IS null)
AND recordedby IS NOT NULL
AND decimallatitude >= $minLat
AND decimallatitude <= $maxLat
AND decimallongitude >= $minLon
AND decimallongitude <= $maxLon
GROUP BY 2
ORDER BY 1 DESC
LIMIT 10

SELECT *
FROM explore.gbif
WHERE $__timeFilter(eventdate)
AND decimallatitude >= $minLat
AND decimallatitude <= $maxLat
AND decimallongitude >= $minLon
AND decimallongitude <= $maxLon
AND (tsv @@ websearch_to_tsquery('simple', '$search') OR NULLIF('$search', '') IS null)
ORDER BY eventdate DESC
LIMIT 100
